{"tid":1305001,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家記住八個字：群眾失焦，林鄭笑了","createTime":"2019-07-10T18:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T11:38:52.000Z","uid":154702,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"91a5f08188435d8f0efccc79e7aeff993849b982","tid":1305001,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:09:00.000Z","msg":"問大家一句<br />\n烈士為咩而死？連儂牆？定係反送中？<br />\n甚或五大訴求？<br />\n請大家每次行動都聚焦返五大訴求<br />\n放棄留戀硬件嘅情懷<br />\n<br />\n明白大家見到同伴俾人打，俾人不公平對待<br />\n條氣真係好唔順<br />\n我都越睇越嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但好肯定咁同你講<br />\n對家已經搵到我哋留戀硬件嘅弱點<br />\n並慢慢組織攻勢<br />\n<br />\n返個幾年教會，聽過基督徒有一句金句<br />\n「眾人以為美的事，要留心去作」<br />\n有好多事情看似美好<br />\n但可能係幫助敵人打開破口既破綻<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5888e4446f519d158b0d99c46f9502444729bfa","tid":1305001,"uid":191989,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:44:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db89a8d39a66c771635bbbd7b541e4fea1b53bdc","tid":1305001,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5888e4446f519d158b0d99c46f9502444729bfa","tid":1305001,"uid":191989,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:44:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:50:32.000Z","msg":"值唔值唔係我哋有資格去評"},{"pid":"51e983a75dc7dbb973e6fb2236896e7284d96227","tid":1305001,"uid":267461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:56:13.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhhh"},{"pid":"bfd77332923fb3e86fa5da321d2a9011ac9eac62","tid":1305001,"uid":191989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:20:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c647532de73384c9b69c436d0aa88d8fd87c2aaa","tid":1305001,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef72ed1317e1148d5bef686d6d8e1c1faf47ba4","tid"